  m_Name: NeighborJournal_09
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 26
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #9 \u2014 Y t\xE1 t\xEAn Hoa"
  category: 3
  content: "B\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n qu\xE1 t\u1EA3i t\u1EEB ng\xE0y m\xF9ng 8. T\xF4i
    l\xE0m ca li\xEAn t\u1EE5c 36 ti\u1EBFng r\u1ED3i ng\xE3 g\u1EE5c. B\xE1c s\u0129
    tr\u01B0\u1EDFng b\u1EA3o b\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFn
    trong v\xF2ng 6 gi\u1EDD, kh\xF4ng c\xF3 thu\u1ED1c. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i ch\u1EC9
    c\xF2n bi\u1EBFt b\u0103ng b\xF3 v\xE0 an \u1EE7i. T\xF4i b\u1ECF v\u1EC1 nh\xE0
    h\xF4m nay, kh\xF4ng quay l\u1EA1i n\u1EEFa. Xin l\u1ED7i c\xE1c b\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n.
    T\xF4i \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i m\u1EA5y h\u1ED9p thu\u1ED1c v\xE0 b\xF4ng b\u0103ng
    trong t\u1EE7, ai c\u1EA7n th\xEC l\u1EA5y."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
